1. *Njujorku* smo posetili pre dve godine. (We visited New York two years ago.)
2. *Njujorku* smo prvi put posetili u prošloj godini. (We visited New York for the first time last year.)
3. *Njujorku* ćemo posetiti u leto. (We will visit New York in the summer.)
4. Prošli put smo u *Njujorku* stigli u avgustu. (We arrived in New York last time in August.)
5. Kako ćemo *Njujorku* obići za vikend? (How will we tour New York over the weekend?)